title: [Desire's Outfitting]
description: A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the painted white plaster walls, and a wide-planked white cedar ceiling rises overhead.  An iron candelabra sits in one corner of a black-checked white tile floor.  There is some hammered copper display hooks on one side of the shop.
